      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d118n1-ptr" id="PJA04d118n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Not found.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d118n2-ptr" id="PJA04d118n2">2</a>
      
   <p>David Waterbury was made brigadier general of Connecticut troops on 3 June (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Francis B. Heitman, comp., &lt;i&gt;Historical Register of Officers of the Continental Army during the War of the Revolution&lt;/i&gt;, new edn., Washington, 1914. ]">Heitman, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Register Continental Army</span></span>, p. 574).</p>

